Install from NuGet Gallery or run command in terminal with the .NET version matching your api.csproj:
    MicrosoftEntityFrameworkCore.SqlServer
        cd api 
        dotnet add package Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.SqlServer --version 8.0.0

    MicrosoftEntityFrameworkCore.Tools
        cd api
        dotnet add package Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Tools --version 8.0.0

    MicrosoftEntityFrameworkCore.Design
        cd api
        dotnet add package Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Design --version 8.0.0

Check Nuget packages installed tab that all packages have been installed.
It may take some time to load into the NugetGallery